<p class="ql-align-center"> 料峭寒冬刚刚拉开序幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进入后疫情时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高新医院消化科仍秉持着那份义无反顾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一往无前的勇气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/d4b70768467747e394cdd20d71f5fb07.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
